persons.name: mark j. rebilas mark j. rebilas-usa

text:
Feb 23, 2017 at 7:45a ET 0Shares The greatest and the goofiest. 
MLB spring training is here, meaning its time for another round of God's gift to photography: baseball team pictures. 
Teams throughout the league continue to send in the results of their roster shoots, and the following are 25 of the greatest individual (and joint!) head shots of the 2017 MLB season. 
We do not deserve Colby Rasmus or his disgusting neck beard. Kyle Schwarber is ... Shrub Man 
Mark J. Rebilas Mark J. Rebilas-USA TODAY Sports Jackie Bradley Jr. and the most puppy face
